      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. it feels like we’re just watching a slow motion car crash and everyone is pretending it’s not happening. what’s even the point of trying to build a life or a career or anything when the foundation is literally crumbling? it feels so pointless to keep going when the world is just... dying.",
